ðŸ’¡ Overview

This project is a **modular Music Player service** built using **SwiftUI**, **Combine**, and classic **design patterns** (Strategy + Singleton). It supports music playback from two sources:

- Local Files (mock)
- Spotify (mock API)

Built with MVVM architecture and reactive UI updates using Combine.




